                                                   -0.44445995988105
    0.89008358737875       1    0.45789763178724
    &END 
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 12.0
  &END POTENTIAL

  &POWELL
     ACCURACY   1.e-14
     STEP_SIZE  0.001
     STEP_SIZE_SCALING  0.900
     MAX_INIT   25
     MAX_FUN    250
     WEIGHT_PSIR0 0.0
